# SIMULATIONS

## Generar Simulacro

POST /simulations/generate

Simulacro Completo

```json
{
  "type": "FULL",
  "isTimed": true
}
```

Simulacro por Área

```json
{
  "type": "AREA",
  "areaId": "uuid",
  "isTimed": true
}
```

Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "attemptId": "uuid",
    "status": "IN_PROGRESS"
  }
}
```

---

## Obtener Simulacro

GET /simulations/:attemptId

Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "id": "uuid",
    "status": "IN_PROGRESS",
    "questions": []
  }
}
```

---

## Guardar Respuesta

POST /simulations/:attemptId/answer

Request

```json
{
  "questionId": "uuid",
  "selectedOptionId": "uuid"
}
```

Response

```json
{
  "success": true
}
```

---

## Finalizar Simulacro

POST /simulations/:attemptId/finish

Response

```json
{
  "success": true,
  "data": {
    "score": 350,
    "correctAnswers": 200,
    "incorrectAnswers": 54
  }
}
```

